  <archetypedescription>           
    <p>
      Rakes are young nobles, the product of too much money and not enough to do.
      Indolent nare-do-wells roaming the lands, living off their wits
      and their quick reactions, looking for adventure and a handfull of silver
      where ever they might find it.  
    </p>
